      "content": "i don't know if a \"story\" is worth telling if it's just this. it's just exhausting. if i just stopped... if i just let go... it wouldn't be a tragedy or anything. no one would even call a phone or notice a void. it would just be quiet. wouldn't that be easier for everyone? just a quiet exit that doesn't disrupt anything?",
